sub_title: English Teacher in Adult Education: Business, Academic, General and Conversational English, and English for Specific Purposes (e.g. English for Customer Services, Hospitality, Aviation & Tourism, Administration, etc.)
summary:
Freelance language teacher and trainer (group, online and private lessons). I teach the following:
- Business English
- English for Specific Purposes, e.g. Administration, Hospitality and Tourism, Reception, Customer Service, etc.
- General English
- Cambridge English
- Conversational English
- Business Writing
- Academic Writing
- Conversational Afrikaans
